  "marketPositioning": "Linera positions itself as a Layer 1 \"Real-Time Blockchain\" specifically optimized for high-performance Web3 applications that require predictable, low-latency interactions and internet-scale capacity. Its unique microchain architecture, providing dedicated chains per user or application, is a key differentiator compared to traditional monolithic blockchains and even other scalable multi-chain or modular approaches. It aims to solve the blockspace scarcity problem and offer a developer-friendly environment for building responsive decentralized applications, drawing on expertise from high-performance payment protocol research."
